# DigiOne — Master Roadmap (prioritized)

Reordered 2026-06-14. Goal: **get most things production-ready before go-live.** The order is
dependency-aware — foundations that de-risk everything come first, then the revenue path, then
growth features, then hardening; mobile is last. `(was N)` = your original number.

Why this order, in one line: **you can't safely build or ship features without (a) a place to
test them and (b) a way to deploy them — so those come before the features themselves; and you
refactor for maintainability *before* piling on more code, not after.**

Cross-refs: DB/test details live in `6(left)-2026-06-14-post-dashboard-followups.md`;
storage items in `1(left)-2026-06-03-storage-followups.md`; the shipped DB work in
`5(done)-2026-06-13-db-production-audit.md`.

