## PHASE 1 — Auth & identity (users can't transact without this; it gates the money path)

**4. Login / Signup / Forgot-password** (was 12)
Finish the auth surface — **forgot-password / reset flow** is the likely gap. Needs a
transactional-email provider (Resend/Postmark/SES) wired for reset + receipts. Deps: #1–#3.
Effort: M.

**5. OAuth integration** (was 13)
Extend auth with Google (and any others). Callback + `app_metadata.role` promotion already exist;
verify per `.claude/rules/google-oauth-reference.md`. Deps: #4. Effort: S–M.

**6. Dashboard Profile + KYC** (was 11)
Profile editing + KYC capture/verify. **KYC gates payouts** (the money path), so it's required
before real creators withdraw. Deps: #4. Effort: M.

> **+ Added 1a — Transactional email** (provider + templates: verify, reset, receipt, payout
> notice). Required by #4 and the receipt/notification flows.

