## PHASE 3 — Growth features (differentiators; valuable but not blocking core revenue)

**10. AI integration** (was 16)
AI in site creation + other surfaces. You want this before prod — mid priority. Pick a model
(default to latest Claude), design the prompt/agent surface, mind cost/rate limits. Deps: #7–#8.
Effort: L.

**11. Instagram automation** (was 9)
Note: the `20260418_insta_autodm` migration is a *phantom* (registered, tables not live — see
`6(left)…` C3). Decide the real schema first, then build. Deps: #4 (auth), provider/API access.
Effort: L.

**12. Other automation** (was 10)
Email / WhatsApp / Telegram / Google-Sheets flows. Deps: #11 patterns + #1a email. Effort: L.

