## PHASE 4 — Ops tooling & hardening (the pre-production gate)

**13. Admin panel / production tools** (was 3)
Start **minimal** (refunds, user/payout management, support lookups) — you need ops tools before
real users, even if small. `is_super_admin()` read-RLS is already in place. Deps: #6, #7. Effort: M–L.

**14. Cloudflare security** (was 14)
WAF, bot/rate protection, DDoS, proxy. Deps: #2 (deploy/domain). Effort: M.

**15. CDN** (was 15)
Asset/image CDN (Cloudflare or Supabase Storage CDN). Deps: #14. Effort: S–M.

